OL,3,C22-year-old man charged with murder
OL,4,Cafter death in Welsh town
OL,6,FA 22-year-old man has been charged
OL,7,Fwith murder following a death in
OL,8,FWelshpool town centre.
OL,10,FMartin Slezak, of Stanley Street,
OL,11,FWelshpool, has been charged with the
OL,12,Fmurder of 49-year-old Young John
OL,13,FMongan from Walsall.
OL,15,FDyfed-Powys Police were called to
OL,16,FChurch Street at approximately 1am on
OL,17,FSunday (28 June) after reports that a
OL,18,Fman had been injured, however he later
OL,19,Fdied at the scene.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/2
