OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1782906493
OL,3,C22-year-old man charged with murder
OL,4,Cafter death in Welsh town
OL,6,FThe force confirmed that Slezak has
OL,7,Fbeen remanded in custody and is due to
OL,8,Fappear at court.
OL,10,FA statement issued by police said:
OL,11,F"There will continue to be a police
OL,12,Fpresence in the town centre over the
OL,13,Ffollowing days."
OL,15,FThey also thanked all those who had
OL,16,Fassisted with the investigation so far.
